<section id="why" class="mt-[84px] rounded-[30px] bg-panel px-[30px] py-[64px] sm:px-[58px]">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[720px] text-center">
    <h2 class="text-[38px] font-extrabold tracking-[-0.02em] text-card">Why it's free</h2>
    <div class="my-[24px] space-y-[18px] text-[19px] leading-[1.65] text-left text-[#e6dfd9]">
      <p>
      Budgeting is critical when money is tight - but most apps
      charge a monthly subscription that's out of reach for the people who need it most.
      Trackie is free so that cost is never the reason someone
      can't get on top of their money.
      </p>
      <p>Trackie is hosted by <a href="https://github.com/alangrainger" class="font-semibold text-white underline underline-offset-2">Alan Grainger</a>.
        I've received so much value from the NZ personal
      finance community over the years, and this is a way for me to give back.
      I will never monetise this - it will always be free for anyone in New Zealand who needs it.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
